import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import GeneralBanner from '../Common/BannerParts/GeneralBanner';
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

class BasementRenovationInRichmondHill extends Component {
  static propTypes = {
  };

  state = {
  };

  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Helmet>
          <title>AGM Basements | Basement Renovation In Richmond Hill</title>
        </Helmet>
        <GeneralBanner title="Basement Renovation in Richmond Hill" />
        <div className="container mt-5">
          <p>For those in Richmond Hill seeking basement remodelling of the highest quality, there’s no substitute for AGM Basements. As industry experts, we have completed countless basement renovations in the area to exceptional standards, ensuring high customer satisfaction.</p>

          <h3>Basement renovations to any brief</h3>

          <p>AGM boasts an outstanding portfolio of completed projects with a huge variety of complexity and features, which means we are confident in our ability to create exactly the space you desire on time and to budget. Our experienced and personable team work alongside our clients every step of the way to ensure complete customer satisfaction, and that is something we are proud to guarantee.</p>

          <p>AGM have assembled a team of tremendous quality and experience over the last 18 years, meaning we only work alongside the best basement contractors, interior designers, builders and electricians. Our track record of providing satisfaction throughout the build journey means our service within the region is of unparalleled quality, and countless past customers will tell you the same thing!</p>

          <p>Rest assured there is no job too big or too small. With our talented team of basement builders, we can transform your renovated basement into your new favourite room.</p>

          <p>Some of the projects we have worked on in the past include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Kitchens</li>
            <li>Fireplaces</li>
            <li>Saunas</li>
            <li>Bars</li>
            <li>Wine cellars</li>
            <li>Why choose us?</li>
          </ul>
          <p>AGM is a company you can trust to deliver your vision for your basement. Our 100% customer satisfaction guarantee means you need not worry about the finished product and we recommend all potential customers attend one of our various open houses or finishing showcases to experience the quality we can instil in your home.</p>

          <h3>The benefits of basement renovations</h3>

          <p>Whatever the reason for your renovation it brings a number of benefits. Soon you will be able to boast about the additional value brought to your home, the extra space, and being able to skirt complicated zoning codes. What’s more, basement renovations are much more affordable compared to other kinds of home renovation options.</p>

          <h3>Customer satisfaction guarantee</h3>

          <p>Customer satisfaction and safety are our chief concerns. That’s why we undertake a number of measures to ensure your project meets our stringent quality and safety standards. These include our signature water seal, our total seal for mould and rust as well as our total seal for radon, ensuring that your basement stays in peak condition and looking good for years to come.</p>

          <p>We won’t take a penny of your payment from you until you sign off, and we are proud to be able to meet your deadline or we will pay you! Please get in touch to take advantage of our free estimate service and allow us to demonstrate the quality and value that AGM can bring to your basement remodelling in Richmond Hill.</p>
        </div>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default BasementRenovationInRichmondHill;
